import {Button, Modal, Container, Row, Col,} from 'react-bootstrap'
import React from 'react'
import BrickModal from './BrickModal'

export const textColors = {
    A: '#6d4c41',
    B: '#e53935',
    C: '#d81b60',
    D: '#8e24aa',
    E: '#3949ab',
    F: '#1e88e5',
    G: '#039be5',
    H: '#00acc1',
    I: '#00897b',   
    J: '#43a047',
    K: '#7cb342',
    L: '#120078',
    M: '#9d0191',
    N: '#fd3a69',
    O: '#fecd1a',
    P: '#ffa45b',
    Q: '#fbf6f0',
    R: '#aee6e6',
    S: '#34626c',
    T: '#839b97',
    U: '#cfd3ce',
    V: '#c6b497',
    W: '#30475e',
    X: '#5c6e91',
    Y: '#8f384d',
    Z: '#dd9866'
}


function ModalTemp({show, select}) {    
    
  const closeModal = () => {select()};
    
    return (
             
        <Modal animation={false} show={show} onHide={closeModal}>
          <Modal.Header closeButton>
            <Modal.Title>Abecedario</Modal.Title>
          </Modal.Header>
          <Modal.Body>
            <Container>
              <Row className="justify-content-md-center">
                <Col xs lg="3"><BrickModal color={'#green'} text={'A'} size="sm" /></Col>
                <Col xs lg="3"><BrickModal color={'#e53935'} text={'B'} size="sm" /></Col>
                <Col xs lg="3"><BrickModal color={'#d81b60'} text={'C'} size="sm" /></Col>
                <Col xs lg="3"><BrickModal color={'#8e24aa'} text={'D'} size="sm" /></Col>
              </Row>
              <Row className="justify-content-md-center">
                <Col xs lg="3"><BrickModal color={'#3949ab'} text={'E'} size="sm" /></Col>
                <Col xs lg="3"><BrickModal color={'#1e88e5'} text={'F'} size="sm" /></Col>
                <Col xs lg="3"><BrickModal color={'#7cb342'} text={'G'} size="sm" /></Col>
                <Col xs lg="3"><BrickModal color={'#00acc1'} text={'H'} size="sm" /></Col>
              </Row>
              <Row className="justify-content-md-center">
                <Col xs lg="3"><BrickModal color={'#00897b'} text={'I'} size="sm" /></Col>
                <Col xs lg="3"><BrickModal color={'#43a047'} text={'J'} size="sm" /></Col>
                <Col xs lg="3"><BrickModal color={'#039be5'} text={'K'} size="sm" /></Col>
                <Col xs lg="3"><BrickModal color={'#120078'} text={'L'} size="sm" /></Col>
              </Row>
              <Row className="justify-content-md-center">
                <Col xs lg="3"><BrickModal color={'#9d0191'} text={'M'} size="sm" /></Col>
                <Col xs lg="3"><BrickModal color={'#fd3a69'} text={'N'} size="sm" /></Col>
                <Col xs lg="3"><BrickModal color={'#fecd1a'} text={'O'} size="sm" /></Col>
                <Col xs lg="3"><BrickModal color={'#ffa45b'} text={'P'} size="sm" /></Col>
              </Row>
              <Row className="justify-content-md-center">
                <Col xs lg="3"><BrickModal color={'#fbf6f0'} text={'Q'} size="sm" /></Col>
                <Col xs lg="3"><BrickModal color={'#aee6e6'} text={'R'} size="sm" /></Col>
                <Col xs lg="3"><BrickModal color={'#34626c'} text={'S'} size="sm" /></Col>
                <Col xs lg="3"><BrickModal color={'#839b97'} text={'T'} size="sm" /></Col>
              </Row>
              <Row className="justify-content-md-center">
                <Col xs lg="3"><BrickModal color={'#6d4c41'} text={'U'} size="sm" /></Col>
                <Col xs lg="3"><BrickModal color={'#e53935'} text={'V'} size="sm" /></Col>
                <Col xs lg="3"><BrickModal color={'#d81b60'} text={'W'} size="sm" /></Col>
                <Col xs lg="3"><BrickModal color={'#8e24aa'} text={'X'} size="sm" /></Col>
              </Row>
              <Row className="justify-content-md-center">
                <Col xs lg="3"><BrickModal color={'#8f384d'} text={'Y'} size="sm" /></Col>
                <Col xs lg="3"><BrickModal color={'#dd9866'} text={'Z'} size="sm" /></Col>
                </Row>
            </Container>

          </Modal.Body>
          <Modal.Footer>            
            <Button variant="primary" onClick={closeModal}>
              Enviar Palabra
            </Button>
          </Modal.Footer>
        </Modal>
      
    );
  }

  export default ModalTemp
